<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>ḥzyn mjrwḥ</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- ḥzyn mjrwḥ wfyn mạ ạ̉rwḥ ʿdẖạb ạlrwḥ mlạzmny
 wjrḥ kbyr wqlb ạ̉syr dẖnwby ktyr bthzmny
 1- bdạyty fy ạlṭryq kạnt ywm mạ rfḍt fạdy
 brgẖm ậlạmh kạn sạkt wạ̉nạ ạlly ṣlbth bạ̹ydy
 2- wʿsẖt ḥyạty mn ywmhạ mạ byn ạ̉ḥzạny wdmwʿy
 tlwmny nfsy wbạlmwhạ wlsh ạljrḥ fy ḍlwʿy
 3- ạ̉nạ ạlmjrm ạ̉nạ ạljạny wḍhry lldẖnwb mḥny
 ạ̉nạ lạzm ạ̉ʿwd tạny wạ̉qwl lh yạrb sạ mḥny</lyrics>
